| Type                     | Prefix    | Purpose              |
| ------------------------ | --------- | -------------------- |
| **Global Unicast (GUA)** | 2000::/3  | Public, internet     |
| **Link-Local Unicast**   | fe80::/10 | Local LAN only       |
| **Unique Local (ULA)**   | fc00::/7  | Private network      |
| **Multicast**            | ff00::/8  | One-to-many          |
| **Anycast**              | (shared)  | Closest host routing |
| **Loopback**             | ::1       | Local testing        |
| **Unspecified**          | ::        | No address assigned  |
